      <title>苹果在首款色情应用登陆 iPhone 后批评欧盟法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/apple-blasts-eu-app-laws-after-first-porn-app-comes-to-iphones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在首款已知的 iPhone 色情应用程序出现在该地区苹果公司的设备上后，苹果公司严厉批评了欧盟的《数字市场法案》。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/apple-blasts-eu-app-laws-after-first-porn-app-comes-to-iphones</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片销量持续低迷，恩智浦发布令人失望的销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/nxp-gives-disappointing-sales-forecast-as-chip-slump-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[恩智浦半导体公司（NXP Semiconductors NV）给出了令人失望的第一季度营收预测，表明工业和汽车芯片需求低迷的局面仍在持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/nxp-gives-disappointing-sales-forecast-as-chip-slump-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:29:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空客聘请高盛与马斯克合作开发欧洲航天业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/airbus-hires-goldman-for-european-space-tie-up-to-rival-musk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，空中客车集团已聘请高盛集团提供建议，以打造一家新的欧洲太空和卫星公司，从而更好地与埃隆马斯克占据主导地位的 SpaceX 进行竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/airbus-hires-goldman-for-european-space-tie-up-to-rival-musk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:00:47 GMT</pubDate>
